5. Place property in `./config/application.properties` __configuration file__

    &lt;!-- language: lang-pl --&gt;

        server.port=7788

    and run:

    &lt;!-- language: lang-bash --&gt;

         java -jar &lt;path/to/my/jar&gt;

6. Place property in `./config/application.yaml`

    &lt;!-- language: lang-json --&gt;

        server:
